Pivot charts are graphical representation of pivot table.

NOrmally the difference b/w bar chart and pivot chart is that it provides us with filter options
inside of the chart.

For creation of pivot chart first select the whole table data and  then Goto insert menu
and click on pivot chart option provided and here we will get all the previous pivot charts
we had plotted earlier.

Pivot chart Will give us more reputation as compared to normal  chart if plotted carefully.